<paragraph id="BE1D36A4EE55FF816B8DD1D7FDB8F38F" blockId="19.[151,1436,151,603]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis id="8CD6EAB6EE55FF816B8DD1D7FE14F3E6" bold="true" box="[198,508,151,177]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Distribution and habitat</emphasis>
:—Collected in the western part of the Amazon Basin of 
<collectingCountry id="C6B57634EE55FF816FFCD1D8FB04F3E5" box="[1207,1260,152,178]" name="Peru" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Peru</collectingCountry>
